performances.description: 1) An awesome bluesy jam vehicle.. 2) When the hell did you  ever hear them bust this one out? 3) This is the '73 RFK Show. That should be enough :)
jerry and merle: this is probably one of the best songs jerry ever played. first show back in the states after europe 72 please listen to this!
Awkward but good version, major bustout, not played since RFK 73.
